    <string name="feeling_dizzy_weak_or_extremely_tired">感到頭暈、虛弱或極度疲倦</string>
    <string name="headache_that_feels_worse_when_you_stand_up">站起來時頭痛加劇</string>
    <string name="if_you_notice_these_signs_try_to_increase_your_fluid">如果你察覺到這些徵兆，請試著增加液體攝取量。</string>
    <string name="what_and_how_to_drink">飲什麼及如何飲用</string>
    <string name="plain_water_main_choice_sip_often">清水：首選，經常小口飲用。</string>
    <string name="warm_liquids_warm_water_herbal_tea_or_clear_broth_can">溫熱飲品：溫水、花草茶或清湯可以：舒緩喉嚨痛、幫助鬆解黏液，讓你感覺更舒適</string>
    <string name="oral_rehydration_solution_ors_or_electrolyte_drinks_useful_if_you">口服補液鹽溶液（ORS）或電解質飲品：如果你有高燒、嘔吐或腹瀉，這些飲品有助於補充水分和鹽分。避免飲用含糖量過高的飲品。</string>
    <string name="tip_if_you_dont_feel_like_drinking_much_at_once">👉 小貼士：如果你不想一次飲太多，每隔幾分鐘小口啜飲。</string>
