    <string name="drinking_water_at_home_helps_but_you_should_see_a">在家飲水有幫助，但若有以下情況，應看醫生：</string>
    <string name="you_cant_keep_fruits_down_vomit_everything">你無法留住液體（嘔吐一切）</string>
    <string name="you_feel_very_dizzy_confused_or_have_a_very_fast">你感到非常頭暈、意識模糊，或心跳非常快。</string>
    <string name="you_have_trouble_breathing_chest_pain_or_a_high_lasting">你有呼吸困難、胸痛或持續高燒。</string>
    <string name="a_baby_child_pregnant_woman_or_elderly_person_shows_signs">嬰兒、兒童、孕婦或長者出現脫水徵狀。</string>
    <string name="hydration_doesnt_cure_the_illness_but_it_helps_your_body">補充水分不能治癒疾病，但有助身體更好地恢復。</string>
